ChangeLog LodinPay Dolibarr module

v1.0.0 - 2026-03-03
- Initial release
- Automatic RTP payment link generation on invoice validation
- QR code display on invoice card
- Professional PDF model with clickable payment button and QR code
- Payment status synchronization via Sync button
- Auto mark invoice as Paid on payment confirmation
- Invoice PDF automatically sent to LodinPay backend
- lodinpay PDF model set as default on module activation
- Restores previous PDF model on module deactivation
- French and English translations included
- Compatible with Dolibarr 17.x to 22.x
